OL,7,FThere were "serious failings" in the
OL,8,Fprobation supervision of quadruple
OL,9,Fmurderer Joshua Jacques, the Chief
OL,10,FInspector of Probation has said.
OL,12,FJacques, 29, was on probation when he
OL,13,Fattacked Samantha Drummonds and her
OL,14,Ffamily with a knife in their home in
OL,15,FDelaford Road, Bermondsey, south
OL,16,FLondon, early on April 25 2022.
