OL,7,FPolice found the bodies of Ms
OL,8,FDrummonds, 27, her mother Tanysha
OL,9,FOfori-Akuffo, 45, grandmother Dolet
OL,10,FHill, 64, and Ms Hill's partner Denton
OL,11,FBurke, 58, after being alerted to a
OL,12,Fdisturbance by a neighbour.
OL,14,FDuring his trial, the Old Bailey heard
OL,15,Fthat Jacques took 3g of skunk cannabis
OL,16,Fa day and refused to consider cutting
OL,17,Fdown, saying he would carry on smoking
OL,18,Fmarijuana "even if it killed" him.
