OL,7,FJacques had been released on licence
OL,8,Fon November 11 2021, following a 51-
OL,9,Fmonth custodial sentence in 2019 for
OL,10,Fdrug-related offences.
OL,12,FThe judge found that Jacques'
OL,13,Foffending had been contributed to by
OL,14,Fcannabis abuse, and that he was "well
OL,15,Faware" of the impact of it on his
OL,16,Fmental health.
