OL,3,CSerious failings in supervision of
OL,4,CSouth London quadruple murderer says
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,FChief Inspector of Probation Martin
OL,8,FJones, who conducted an independent
OL,9,Freview into Jacques' supervision by
OL,10,Fthe Probation Service, said that it
OL,11,Ffailed to organise a drug abuse
OL,12,Fintervention for Jacques, despite it
OL,13,Fbeing a condition of his release.
OL,15,F"The case records show that Jacques
OL,16,Fwas routinely using cannabis whilst on
OL,17,Fprobation, and his licence contained a
OL,18,Fcondition to engage in a drug abuse
OL,19,Fintervention on release from prison,"
OL,20,Fhe said.
OL,26,@wD@AOU{D@eO]
