OL,3,CSerious failings in supervision of
OL,4,CSouth London quadruple murderer says
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,F"No such intervention was organised by
OL,8,Fthe Probation Service and our
OL,9,Finspection found no evidence of a
OL,10,Freferral to a drugs agency."
OL,12,FMr Jones said the enforcement of
OL,13,FJacques' probation was "inconsistent"
OL,14,Fdespite concerns about repeated non-
OL,15,Fcompliance.
OL,17,F"There were serious failings in the
OL,18,Fsupervision of Joshua Jacques," he
OL,19,Fsaid.
