OL,7,F"Despite concerns about repeated non-
OL,8,Fcompliance with his licence
OL,9,Fconditions, enforcement practice was
OL,10,Finconsistent and opportunities to
OL,11,Frecall Jacques to custody were missed."
OL,13,FHe said that Jacques was incorrectly
OL,14,Fallocated to a newly qualified
OL,15,Fprobation officer, and that management
OL,16,Foversight of the case was
OL,17,F"insufficient".
