OL,7,FJacques was also assessed as posing a
OL,8,F"high risk" of serious harm to the
OL,9,Fpublic before being released from
OL,10,Fcustody, he said, but his risk to
OL,11,Fformer partners or probation staff was
OL,12,F"underestimated".
OL,14,F"No risk assessment was completed for
OL,15,FJacques following his release which
OL,16,Fresulted in no risk management plan or
OL,17,Fsentence plan in the community being
OL,18,Fcompleted," he said.
