OL,7,FJacques himself had reported that
OL,8,F"random aggression" could be a symptom
OL,9,Fof declining mental health, Mr Jones
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"In February 2022, Jacques disclosed
OL,13,Fto probation court staff that he was
OL,14,Fexperiencing a decline in his mental
OL,15,Fhealth; however, no action was taken,"
OL,16,Fhe said.
