OL,3,CSerious failings in supervision of
OL,4,CSouth London quadruple murderer says
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,F"Inspectors found during this review
OL,8,Fthat probation staff felt ill equipped
OL,9,Fto understand and respond to mental
OL,10,Fhealth concerns, with limited training
OL,11,Fand support being available to them."
OL,13,FMr Jones said that the case was
OL,14,F"symptomatic" of issues observed
OL,15,Facross the Probation Service in recent
OL,16,Fyears.
