OL,4,CSouth London quadruple murderer says
OL,5,Cwatchdog
OL,7,F"A reliance on an inexperienced cohort
OL,8,Fof probation staff, a lack of support
OL,9,Ffor mental health and substance misuse
OL,10,Fissues alongside insufficient
OL,11,Fmanagement oversight are concerns
OL,12,Fwhich have been highlighted
OL,13,Frepeatedly," he said.
OL,15,F"As a result of this review, eight
OL,16,Frecommendations were made to HMPPS (HM
OL,17,FPrison and Probation Service). They
OL,18,Fhave accepted all these
OL,19,Frecommendations and responded with an
OL,20,Faction plan for implementing them."
