OL,7,F"It's no use the Lord Chancellor
OL,8,Fcalling for a review if he isn't going
OL,9,Fto follow up with the necessary
OL,10,Faction. We have a mismanaged Probation
OL,11,FService that is already struggling to
OL,12,Fretain experienced staff.
OL,14,F"These issues have been made worse by
OL,15,Fthe fact that the Government has
OL,16,Fresorted to emergency measures to
OL,17,Fmanage the prison capacity crisis
OL,18,Fwhich have loaded more cases on to the
OL,19,FProbation Service."
